      "para_id": "Q001909.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(1') For ... Lu-Utu , the stone-cutter , fashioned ( this ) beautiful bowl for the ... of ..., king of Urim , king of the four quarters ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001909.7",
      "line_range": "7",
      "translation": "(6') The name of this bowl is \" My lady , let me live in his benevolent attention , may he look at me with favour !\""
    }
  ],
